    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, providing an unfiltered analog connection to the road. Key preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the high-torque output reliably. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals remain sharp, and the suspension geometry is dialed for spirited cornering. A well-sorted example for the purist who values visceral performance over show-car aesthetics.",
