      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a beautiful, deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you may find the minor, expected road-wear typical of a well-loved car. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are in excellent shape with plenty of tire tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the seats are firm and supportive with no rips or heavy stains, and the dashboard remains free of any sun damage. Every feature, including the premium audio system, heated seats, and navigation, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet. It has been meticulously maintained with a full service history, including a recent fluid flush and multi-point inspection. It tracks perfectly on the highway and offers a smooth, responsive driving experience. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
